      <div class="responsive-bottom-margin">
          
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr">
      <div class="govspeak">
<div class="call-to-action">
<p>Statutory guidance sets out what schools and local authorities must do to comply with the law. You should follow the guidance unless you have a very good reason not to.
<br><br>
There is some guidance that you must follow without exception. In these cases we make this clear in the guidance document itself.</p>
</div>

<p>There is supporting guidance to help you comply with the law.</p>

<p>These publications reflect the current legal position (unless otherwise indicated), but may not reflect the current government’s policies.</p>

</div>
</div>


